query.commandtext: SELECT *, lb1 / a * 100 bl1, lb2 / a * 100 bl2, lb3 / a * 100 bl3, lb4 / a * 100 bl4, lb5 / a * 100 bl5 FROM ( SELECT cif_no, dep_no, dep_name, kind_no, kind_name, SUM(putout_amt) putout_amt, sum(loan_bal) loan_bal, COUNT(cif_no) a, IFNULL( CASE five_cls_no WHEN '1' THEN count(cif_no) END, 0 ) lb1, IFNULL( CASE five_cls_no WHEN '2' THEN count(cif_no) END, 0 ) lb2, IFNULL( CASE five_cls_no WHEN '3' THEN count(cif_no) END, 0 ) lb3, IFNULL( CASE five_cls_no WHEN '4' THEN count(cif_no) END, 0 ) lb4, IFNULL( CASE five_cls_no WHEN '5' THEN count(cif_no) END, 0 ) lb5, five_cls_name FROM repbasic_business_info WHERE due_beg_date >= ? AND due_beg_date <= ? AND due_state > 2 AND due_state < 5 AND dep_no IN (?) AND CASE ? WHEN '0' THEN 1 = 1 ELSE user_no IN (?) END GROUP BY kind_name ) sss;
SELECT *,CURDATE() AS date FROM (SELECT COM_NAME FROM company_mst)ss;
